- Validation rules require compliance approval
- Workflow rules require ops approval

---

## 14. Performance & Scalability

- Stateless services
- Horizontal scaling
- In-memory rule execution
- Precompiled DSL
- Event-driven integration

---

## 15. Failure Handling

### 15.1 Validation
- Fail fast on REJECT

### 15.2 Workflow
- Retry + timeout handling
- Compensation logic

---

## 16. Anti-Patterns to Avoid

- Mixing rule domains
- Executing DSL directly from DB
- Embedding workflow in rules
- Non-deterministic logic
- Missing version binding

---

